400class StartAttackEvent : public BasicEvent
401{
402 public:
403 StartAttackEvent(Creature* summoner, Creature* owner)
404 : _summonerGuid(summoner->GetGUID()), _owner(owner)
405 {
406 }
407
408 bool Execute(uint64 /*time*/, uint32 /*diff*/) override
409 {
410 _owner->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
411 if (Creature* _summoner = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*_owner, _summonerGuid))
412 if (Unit* target = _summoner->AI()->SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, 300.0f))
413 _owner->AI()->AttackStart(target);
414 return true;
415 }
416
417 private:
418 ObjectGuid _summonerGuid;
419 Creature* _owner;
420};
421
422class boss_voice_of_yogg_saron : public CreatureScript
423{
424 public:
425 boss_voice_of_yogg_saron() : CreatureScript("boss_voice_of_yogg_saron") { }
426
427 struct boss_voice_of_yogg_saronAI : public BossAI
428 {
429 boss_voice_of_yogg_saronAI(Creature* creature) : BossAI(creature, BOSS_YOGG_SARON)
430 {
431 Initialize();
432 SetCombatMovement(false);
433 }
434
435 void Initialize()
436 {
437 _guardiansCount = 0;
438 _guardianTimer = 20000;
439 _illusionShattered = false;
440 }
441
442 void MoveInLineOfSight(Unit* who) override
443
444 {
445 // TODO: MoveInLineOfSight doesn't work for such a big distance
446 if (who->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && me->GetDistance2d(who) < 99.0f && !me->IsInCombat())
447 me->SetInCombatWithZone();
448 }
449
450 void EnterEvadeMode() override
451 {
452 BossAI::EnterEvadeMode();
453
454 for (uint8 i = DATA_SARA; i <= DATA_MIMIRON_YS; ++i)
455 if (Creature* creature = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(i)))
456 creature->AI()->EnterEvadeMode();
457
458 // not sure, spoken by Sara (sound), regarding to wowwiki Voice whispers it
459 Map::PlayerList const& players = me->GetMap()->GetPlayers();
460 for (Map::PlayerList::const_iterator itr = players.begin(); itr != players.end(); ++itr)
461 if (Player* player = itr->GetSource())
462 {
463 if (events.IsInPhase(PHASE_ONE))
464 Talk(WHISPER_VOICE_PHASE_1_WIPE, player);
465
466 player->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_SANITY);
467 player->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_INSANE);
468 }
469 }
470
471 void Reset() override
472 {
473 _Reset();
474 events.SetPhase(PHASE_ONE);
475
476 instance->SetData(DATA_DRIVE_ME_CRAZY, uint32(true));
477 instance->DoStopTimedAchievement(ACHIEVEMENT_TIMED_TYPE_EVENT, ACHIEV_TIMED_START_EVENT);
478
479 Initialize();
480
481 bool clockwise = false;
482 std::list<TempSummon*> clouds;
483 me->SummonCreatureGroup(CREATURE_GROUP_CLOUDS, &clouds);
484 clouds.sort(Trinity::ObjectDistanceOrderPred(me, true));
485 for (std::list<TempSummon*>::const_iterator itr = clouds.begin(); itr != clouds.end(); ++itr)
486 {
487 (*itr)->AI()->DoAction(int32(clockwise));
488 clockwise = !clockwise;
489 }
490 }
491
492 void EnterCombat(Unit* /*who*/) override
493 {
494 if (Creature* sara = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_SARA)))
495 sara->SetInCombatWith(me);
496
497 for (uint8 i = DATA_FREYA_YS; i <= DATA_MIMIRON_YS; ++i)
498 if (Creature* keeper = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(i)))
499 keeper->SetInCombatWith(me);
500
501 instance->DoStartTimedAchievement(ACHIEVEMENT_TIMED_TYPE_EVENT, ACHIEV_TIMED_START_EVENT);
502
503 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_SUMMON_GUARDIAN_2, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1);
504 DoCast(me, SPELL_SANITY_PERIODIC);
505
506 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LOCK_DOOR, 15000);
507 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_GUARDIAN_OF_YOGG_SARON, _guardianTimer, 0, PHASE_ONE);
508 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_EXTINGUISH_ALL_LIFE, 900000); // 15 minutes
509 }
510
511 void JustDied(Unit* killer) override
512 {
513 // don't despawn Yogg-Saron's corpse, remove him from SummonList!
514 if (Creature* yogg = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(BOSS_YOGG_SARON)))
515 summons.Despawn(yogg);
516
517 BossAI::JustDied(killer);
518 }
519
520 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
521 {
522 if (!UpdateVictim())
523 return;
524
525 events.Update(diff);
526 // don't summon tentacles when illusion is shattered, delay them
527 if (_illusionShattered)
528 events.DelayEvents(diff, EVENT_GROUP_SUMMON_TENTACLES);
529
530 while (uint32 eventId = events.ExecuteEvent())
531 {
532 switch (eventId)
533 {
534 case EVENT_LOCK_DOOR:
535 DoCast(me, SPELL_INSANE_PERIODIC);
536 instance->SetBossState(BOSS_YOGG_SARON, IN_PROGRESS);
537 break;
538 case EVENT_EXTINGUISH_ALL_LIFE:
539 if (Creature* yogg = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(BOSS_YOGG_SARON)))
540 {
541 yogg->AI()->Talk(EMOTE_YOGG_SARON_EXTINGUISH_ALL_LIFE, me);
542 yogg->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, SPELL_EXTINGUISH_ALL_LIFE, true);
543 }
544 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_EXTINGUISH_ALL_LIFE, 10000); // cast it again after a short while, players can survive
545 break;
546 case EVENT_SUMMON_GUARDIAN_OF_YOGG_SARON:
547 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_SUMMON_GUARDIAN_2, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1);
548 ++_guardiansCount;
549 if (_guardiansCount <= 6 && _guardiansCount % 3 == 0)
550 _guardianTimer -= 5000;
551 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_GUARDIAN_OF_YOGG_SARON, _guardianTimer, 0, PHASE_ONE);
552 break;
553 case EVENT_SUMMON_CORRUPTOR_TENTACLE:
554 DoCastAOE(SPELL_CORRUPTOR_TENTACLE_SUMMON);
555 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_CORRUPTOR_TENTACLE, 30000, EVENT_GROUP_SUMMON_TENTACLES, PHASE_TWO);
556 break;
557 case EVENT_SUMMON_CONSTRICTOR_TENTACLE:
558 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_CONSTRICTOR_TENTACLE, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1);
559 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_CONSTRICTOR_TENTACLE, 25000, EVENT_GROUP_SUMMON_TENTACLES, PHASE_TWO);
560 break;
561 case EVENT_SUMMON_CRUSHER_TENTACLE:
562 DoCastAOE(SPELL_CRUSHER_TENTACLE_SUMMON);
563 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_CRUSHER_TENTACLE, 60000, EVENT_GROUP_SUMMON_TENTACLES, PHASE_TWO);
564 break;
565 case EVENT_ILLUSION:
566 {
567 if (Creature* yogg = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(BOSS_YOGG_SARON)))
568 {
569 yogg->AI()->Talk(EMOTE_YOGG_SARON_MADNESS);
570 yogg->AI()->Talk(SAY_YOGG_SARON_MADNESS);
571 }
572
573 me->SummonCreatureGroup(CREATURE_GROUP_PORTALS_10);
574 if (me->GetMap()->Is25ManRaid())
575 me->SummonCreatureGroup(CREATURE_GROUP_PORTALS_25);
576
577 uint8 illusion = urand(CHAMBER_ILLUSION, STORMWIND_ILLUSION);
578 instance->SetData(DATA_ILLUSION, illusion);
579
580 if (Creature* brain = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_BRAIN_OF_YOGG_SARON)))
581 brain->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_INDUCE_MADNESS);
582 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_ILLUSION, 80000, 0, PHASE_TWO); // wowwiki says 80 secs, wowhead says something about 90 secs
583 break;
584 }
585 case EVENT_SUMMON_IMMORTAL_GUARDIAN:
586 DoCastAOE(SPELL_IMMORTAL_GUARDIAN);
587 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_IMMORTAL_GUARDIAN, 15000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
588 break;
589 default:
590 break;
591 }
592 }
593 }
594
595 void DoAction(int32 action) override
596 {
597 switch (action)
598 {
599 case ACTION_PHASE_TRANSFORM:
600 events.SetPhase(PHASE_TRANSFORM);
601 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD);
602 break;
603 case ACTION_PHASE_TWO:

611 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_ILLUSION, 60000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
612 break;
613 case ACTION_TOGGLE_SHATTERED_ILLUSION:
614 _illusionShattered = !_illusionShattered;
615 break;
616 case ACTION_PHASE_THREE:
617 events.SetPhase(PHASE_THREE);
618 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_IMMORTAL_GUARDIAN, 1000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
619 break;
620 default:
621 break;
622 }

763 {

765 return;
766

771

773 return;

776 {

778 {
779 case EVENT_SARAS_FERVOR:

781 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARAS_FERVOR, 6000, 0, PHASE_ONE);
782 break;
783 case EVENT_SARAS_ANGER:
784 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_SARAS_ANGER_TARGET_SELECTOR, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1);
785 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARAS_ANGER, urand(6000, 8000), 0, PHASE_ONE);
786 break;
787 case EVENT_SARAS_BLESSING:
788 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_SARAS_BLESSING_TARGET_SELECTOR, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1);
789 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARAS_BLESSING, urand(6000, 30000), 0, PHASE_ONE);
790 break;
791 case EVENT_TRANSFORM_1:
792 Talk(SAY_SARA_TRANSFORM_2);
793 break;
794 case EVENT_TRANSFORM_2:
795 Talk(SAY_SARA_TRANSFORM_3);
796 break;
797 case EVENT_TRANSFORM_3:
798 Talk(SAY_SARA_TRANSFORM_4);
799 DoCast(me, SPELL_FULL_HEAL);
800 me->setFaction(16);
801 if (Creature* voice = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_VOICE_OF_YOGG_SARON)))
802 voice->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_PHASE_TWO);
803 if (Creature* mimiron = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_YS)))
804 mimiron->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_PHASE_TWO);
805 break;
806 case EVENT_TRANSFORM_4:
807 DoCast(me, SPELL_PHASE_2_TRANSFORM);
808 if (Creature* yogg = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(BOSS_YOGG_SARON)))
809 DoCast(yogg, SPELL_RIDE_YOGG_SARON_VEHICLE);
810 DoCast(me, SPELL_SHADOWY_BARRIER_SARA);
811 _events.SetPhase(PHASE_TWO);
812 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEATH_RAY, 20000, 0, PHASE_TWO); // almost never cast at scheduled time, why?
813 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MALADY_OF_THE_MIND, 18000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
814 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PSYCHOSIS, 1, 0, PHASE_TWO);
815 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BRAIN_LINK, 23000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
816 break;
817 case EVENT_DEATH_RAY:
818 DoCast(me, SPELL_DEATH_RAY);
819 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEATH_RAY, 21000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
820 break;
821 case EVENT_MALADY_OF_THE_MIND:
822 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_MALADY_OF_THE_MIND, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1);
823 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MALADY_OF_THE_MIND, urand(18000, 25000), 0, PHASE_TWO);
824 break;
825 case EVENT_PSYCHOSIS:
826 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_PSYCHOSIS, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1);
827 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PSYCHOSIS, 4000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
828 break;
829 case EVENT_BRAIN_LINK:
830 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_BRAIN_LINK, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 2);
831 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BRAIN_LINK, urand(23000, 26000), 0, PHASE_TWO);
832 break;
833 default:
834 break;

839 void JustSummoned(Creature* summon) override
840 {

842

844 {

846 Talk(SAY_SARA_DEATH_RAY);
847 summon->CastSpell(summon, SPELL_DEATH_RAY_ORIGIN_VISUAL);
848 for (uint8 i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
849 {
850 Position pos;
851 float radius = frand(25.0f, 50.0f);
852 float angle = frand(0.0f, 2.0f * float(M_PI));
853 pos.m_positionX = YoggSaronSpawnPos.GetPositionX() + radius * cosf(angle);
854 pos.m_positionY = YoggSaronSpawnPos.GetPositionY() + radius * sinf(angle);
855 pos.m_positionZ = me->GetMap()->GetHeight(me->GetPhaseMask(), pos.GetPositionX(), pos.GetPositionY(), YoggSaronSpawnPos.GetPositionZ() + 5.0f);
856 me->SummonCreature(NPC_DEATH_RAY, pos, TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN, 20000);
857 }
858 break;
859 case NPC_DEATH_RAY:
860 summon->CastSpell(summon, SPELL_DEATH_RAY_WARNING_VISUAL);
861 break;
862 }
863
864 if (Creature* voice = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_VOICE_OF_YOGG_SARON)))
865 voice->AI()->JustSummoned(summon);
866 }

876 break;

901 void Reset() override
902 {
903 _events.Reset();
904 _events.SetPhase(PHASE_TWO);
905 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_YELL_BOW_DOWN, 3000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
906 DoCast(me, SPELL_SHADOWY_BARRIER_YOGG);
907 DoCast(me, SPELL_KNOCK_AWAY);
908
909 me->ResetLootMode();
910 uint32 keepersCount = _instance->GetData(DATA_KEEPERS_COUNT);
911 if (keepersCount == 0)
912 me->AddLootMode(LOOT_MODE_HARD_MODE_4);
913 if (keepersCount <= 1)
914 me->AddLootMode(LOOT_MODE_HARD_MODE_3);
915 if (keepersCount <= 2)
916 me->AddLootMode(LOOT_MODE_HARD_MODE_2);
917 if (keepersCount <= 3)
918 me->AddLootMode(LOOT_MODE_HARD_MODE_1);
919 }
920
921 void SpellHit(Unit* /*caster*/, SpellInfo const* spell) override
922 {
923 if (spell->Id == SPELL_IN_THE_MAWS_OF_THE_OLD_GOD)
924 me->AddLootMode(32);
925 }
926
927 void JustDied(Unit* /*killer*/) override
928 {
929 Talk(SAY_YOGG_SARON_DEATH);
930
931 if (Creature* creature = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_VOICE_OF_YOGG_SARON)))
932 me->Kill(creature);
933
934 for (uint8 i = DATA_SARA; i <= DATA_BRAIN_OF_YOGG_SARON; ++i)
935 if (Creature* creature = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(i)))
936 creature->DisappearAndDie();
937
938 for (uint8 i = DATA_FREYA_YS; i <= DATA_MIMIRON_YS; ++i)
939 if (Creature* creature = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(i)))
940 creature->AI()->EnterEvadeMode();
941
942 Map::PlayerList const& players = me->GetMap()->GetPlayers();
943 for (Map::PlayerList::const_iterator itr = players.begin(); itr != players.end(); ++itr)
944 if (Player* player = itr->GetSource())
945 {
946 player->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_SANITY);
947 player->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_INSANE);
948 }
949 }
950
951 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
952 {
953 _events.Update(diff);
954
955 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
956 return;
957
958 while (uint32 eventId = _events.ExecuteEvent())
959 {
960 switch (eventId)
961 {
962 case EVENT_YELL_BOW_DOWN:
963 Talk(SAY_YOGG_SARON_SPAWN);
964 break;
965 case EVENT_SHADOW_BEACON:
966 DoCastAOE(SPELL_SHADOW_BEACON);
967 Talk(EMOTE_YOGG_SARON_EMPOWERING_SHADOWS);
968 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHADOW_BEACON, 45000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
969 break;
970 case EVENT_LUNATIC_GAZE:
971 DoCast(me, SPELL_LUNATIC_GAZE);
972 CreatureTextMgr::SendSound(me, SOUND_LUNATIC_GAZE, CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_YELL);
973 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LUNATIC_GAZE, 12000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
974 break;
975 case EVENT_DEAFENING_ROAR:
976 DoCastAOE(SPELL_DEAFENING_ROAR);
977 Talk(SAY_YOGG_SARON_DEAFENING_ROAR);
978 Talk(EMOTE_YOGG_SARON_DEAFENING_ROAR);
979 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEAFENING_ROAR, urand(20000, 25000), 0, PHASE_THREE); // timer guessed
980 break;
981 default:
982 break;
983 }
984 }
985 }
986
987 void DoAction(int32 action) override
988 {
989 switch (action)
990 {
991 case ACTION_PHASE_THREE:
992 _events.SetPhase(PHASE_THREE);
993 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHADOW_BEACON, 45000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
994 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LUNATIC_GAZE, 12000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
995 if (me->GetMap()->Is25ManRaid() && _instance->GetData(DATA_KEEPERS_COUNT) < 4)
996 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEAFENING_ROAR, urand(20000, 25000), 0, PHASE_THREE); // timer guessed
997 Talk(SAY_YOGG_SARON_PHASE_3);
998 DoCast(me, SPELL_PHASE_3_TRANSFORM);
999 me->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_SHADOWY_BARRIER_YOGG);
1000 me->ResetPlayerDamageReq();
1001 break;
1002 default:
1003 break;
1004 }
1005 }

1009 InstanceScript* _instance;

1042 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(true);
1043 DoCastAOE(SPELL_SHATTERED_ILLUSION_REMOVE, true);

1075 _instance->HandleGameObject(_instance->GetGuidData(i), false);
